steps.name: Click on 'New Item' on the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Click on the 'Logo' icon with long pause and return to Main page
Click 'Changes', 'Console Output', 'Edit Build Information', 'Delete build', 'Replay', 'Pipeline Steps' and 'Workspaces' on build drop-down menu
Get a page name from the breadcrumb
